@resource(aws.acm.Certificate, ServerCertificate)
Name: server-acm-certificate
Domain name: app.{domain_name}
Validation method: DNS

@resource(aws.route53.Record, ValidationRecord)
In $HostedZone
The name, type and records are derived from the $ServerCertificate domain validation option.
Ttl: 300

@resource(aws.acm.CertificateValidation, CertificateValidation)
For $ServerCertificate, using $ValidationRecord